    <div class="main review-item" id="5838804">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5838804/" class="title-link">云蒸霞蔚的北洋时代</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5838804"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/53021396/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u53021396-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/53021396/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">枕鱼斋</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-04-09"
      class="main-meta">2013-04-09 13:55:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5838804_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  春日读到了陈钦先生的新著《北洋大时代》，这是一部反映北洋时代的力作。是时，一个民族由懵懂的童年时代走出来，赫然发现了自身的存在，似风华正茂的少年，连举手投足之间都充满了光彩，于春日读到此书，是正当其时。 “北洋”之名始见于宋代，主要指黄海、渤海区域。后来在清...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5838804/#comments">(5回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5838804_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5838804_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5900151">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5900151/" class="title-link">是非功过后人说</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5900151"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/yyyfmmm/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3428097-23.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yyyfmmm/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">晏砚兰心</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-04-27"
      class="main-meta">2013-04-27 12:08:52</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5900151_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  北洋时代，在我的脑海里其实是非常模糊的一个时代，这里面的原因大概就与我们上学时的历史书有关，一个个脸谱化的人物像走马灯一样在一连串的枯燥数字里闪过，能够让自己记得住的，实在是少得可怜，那时上学可读的课外书实在有限，即便有心拓展一下知识层面也不是件易事，好在...

